      "text": "- What are some patterns in large-scale contexts that we didn't address in the Triad of Commoning?\n- What are key unresolved theoretical issues in how commons interact with political economy and society?\n- How can we create systems that support or at least accommodate commoning at larger scales or with more diverse players?\n\n"
    },
